[b]SedexCraft[/b] - A unique and friendly Minecraft server, we strive to have players achieve the best gaming experience with friendly staff and a very simple website and game setup. SedexCraft is a survival server with the ability to PVP with other players while also you are able to create your own towns and nations and be able to protect your self from other griefers and pvpers. We are a small and friendly community and our website is online 99.9% of the time and the server has nearly no lag and downtime at all. If you enjoy building, fighting monsters, fighting other players or just socializing then Sedex is the right server for you.
